snippet.title: War Theatre - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP1594-CUSA11798_00-WARTHEATRE000100

Assemble your forces! War Theatre is a turn-based strategy RPG, featuring seven powerful heroes clashing in a steampunk-inspired world. Complete quests to unlock perks and customize your forces for victory!
